{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "meepleai-api-collection",
		"name": "MeepleAI API Collection",
		"description": "Complete API test collection for MeepleAI - AI board game rules assistant.\n\n**Architecture**: ASP.NET 9, DDD/CQRS with 7 bounded contexts\n\n**Base URL**: `{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n**Authentication**:\n- Cookie-based sessions (httpOnly, secure)\n- API Keys via `Authorization: ApiKey {{api_key}}` header\n- OAuth 2.0 (Google, Discord, GitHub)\n- 2FA/TOTP support\n\n**Version**: 1.0.0\n**Last Updated**: 2025-11-19",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "noauth"
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"// Global pre-request script",
					"// Set timestamp for logging",
					"pm.environment.set('timestamp', new Date().toISOString());"
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"listen": "test",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"// Global test script",
					"// Log response time",
					"console.log('Response time:', pm.response.responseTime, 'ms');"
				]
			}
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:5080",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Health Check",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Health Check",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', function() {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has healthy status', function() {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('Healthy');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["health"]
						},
						"description": "Health check endpoint. Verifies API is running and all dependencies (PostgreSQL, Redis, Qdrant) are accessible."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Health and readiness checks"
		},
